<br>
I have 7 tattoos.  My ancestors are Picts and Comanchees, and whether the art was painted on or tattoed, it was a spiritual thing.  Both sides of my family either/or/and have tattoo art, or at least paint it on for certain ceremonies.  I've a friend who has her totem animal, a crow, tattooed on her shoulder.  Actually a lot of my family members have their &quot;guardian&quot; animal somewhere on their bodies.  <br>
<br>
Each of mine was inked during a turning point in my life.   <p><a href="http://www.geocities.com/danykalla" target="_blank">
<img src="http://pic3.picturetrail.com/VOL18/605666/942834/11687410.jpg"><border="0"></a> <B>And your problem with rangers is...?
