<br>
My tattoo artist freehanded the dragon onto my arm with an ink pencil then tattooed over the drawing. Its shaped sort of like an inverted 'U'. There is a Japanese kanji at the center of the dragon that says 'dragon'. My tattoo is unique, just like me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  There is only one in the world and it decorates my arm. <br>
