<br>
It also says something about you. It shows we're different. You don't ask the same questions I do. You just liked the design, liked tatoos, and so you got it. You didn't think about it like I did, or like I would if I were considering a tatoo. That actually says something, wether you want it to or not. It tells me that we don't think alike about something as permanent as tatoos. <br>
